original_query: SELECT MIN(t.Id) FROM tags as t, posts as p, users as u, votes as v, badges as b WHERE p.Id = t.ExcerptPostId AND u.Id = v.UserId AND u.Id = b.UserId AND u.Id = p.OwnerUserId AND u.Views>=0 AND u.Views<=515 AND u.UpVotes>=0 AND u.CreationDate<=CAST('2014-09-07 13:46:41' AS TIMESTAMP) AND v.BountyAmount>=0 AND v.BountyAmount<=200 AND b.Date<=CAST('2014-09-12 12:56:22' AS TIMESTAMP)
rewritten_query: CREATE VIEW E1 AS SELECT * FROM tags AS tags
CREATE VIEW E2 AS SELECT * FROM posts AS posts
CREATE VIEW E5 AS SELECT * FROM badges AS badges WHERE badges.Date <= TIMESTAMP '2014-09-12 12:56:22'
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E2E5 AS SELECT * FROM E2 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E5 WHERE E2.OwnerUserId=E5.UserId)
CREATE VIEW E4 AS SELECT * FROM votes AS votes WHERE CAST(votes.BountyAmount AS INTEGER) >= 0 AND CAST(votes.BountyAmount AS INTEGER) <= 200
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E2E5E4 AS SELECT * FROM E2E5 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E4 WHERE E2E5.OwnerUserId=E4.UserId)

CREATE VIEW E3 AS SELECT * FROM users AS users WHERE CAST(users.Views AS INTEGER) >= 0 AND CAST(users.Views AS INTEGER) <= 515 AND users.UpVotes >= 0 AND users.CreationDate <= TIMESTAMP '2014-09-07 13:46:41'
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E2E5E4E3 AS SELECT * FROM E2E5E4 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E3 WHERE E2E5E4.OwnerUserId=E3.Id)
CREATE UNLOGGED TABLE E1E2E5E4E3 AS SELECT MIN(Id) AS EXPR$0 FROM E1 WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM E2E5E4E3 WHERE E1.ExcerptPostId=E2E5E4E3.Id)
